  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="2242286">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2242286/" class="title-link">挑错</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2242286"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/elact/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1123727-6.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/elact/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Elact</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-08-18"
      class="main-meta">2009-08-18 00:57:33</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2242286_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  第21页，主人公德文郡公爵。  母亲家族塞西尔，出产小品文作家。  母亲家族的一个名人，译者把他称为公爵的叔叔，他称公爵为侄子。  好像应为翻译成舅舅和外甥。  如果那个名人是公爵的叔叔，那就不是塞西尔家族的人，而是公爵家族的人了。  猜测为UNCLE直译为叔叔，NEPHEW直译...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/2242286/#comments">(2回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_2242286_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_2242286_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



